  - Absent: checkbox, slider, NSTableView, NSScrollView, and real modal sheets (NSAlert/beginSheet/runModal appear nowhere).

  Event/interaction model — Layout catches mouseUp/rightMouseUp/scrollWheel/keyUp → base.blockContaining(point) hit-test →
